{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2525300/extras/Discord.png?t=1739208749\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2525300/extras/ezgif-1-16e32e45e0.gif?t=1739208749\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2525300/extras/Welcome.png?t=1739208749\" />Bahamut and the Waqwaq Tree is a 2D adventure game inspired by Arabian and Middle Eastern mythology. Dive into an immersive underwater realm, explore diverse areas of the cosmic sea, restore the ocean's radiance, and uncover the secrets of an ancient mystery.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2525300/extras/Line_1_1.png?t=1739208749\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2525300/extras/ezgif-1-8dcba08ca9.gif?t=1739208749\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2525300/extras/Worlds.png?t=1739208749\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Immerse yourself in Ma'een, where swimming feels smooth and seamless.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Discover a world full of landmarks, vibrant areas, and ruins of an ancient civilization.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Encounter increasingly challenging obstacles and corruption as you navigate deeper.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2525300/extras/Line_1_1.png?t=1739208749\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2525300/extras/ezgif-1-065d09b0bc.gif?t=1739208749\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2525300/extras/Mechanic.png?t=1739208749\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Harness the power of the light to Illuminate the dark ocean.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Shield yourself from lurking dangers and repell dark entities.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Restore darkened areas and uncover hidden paths.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2525300/extras/Line_1_1.png?t=1739208749\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2525300/extras/ezgif-3-4b882e1712.gif?t=1739208749\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2525300/extras/Solve.png?t=1739208749\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Solve puzzles rooted in the lore of the lost civilization.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Decipher ancient relics and inscriptions.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Unlock the secrets of the forgotten kingdom.</p></li></ul>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2525300/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1739208749","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2525300/page.bg.jpg?t=1739208749","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2525300/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1739208749","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2525300/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1739208749","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22},{"description":"Full controller support","id":28}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"controller_support":"full","detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2525300/ex